div.p: Liber maurusiarum duplicium antehac numquam nistarum artificibus omnibus ut aurificibus phrigionibus vitrarys et id genus artificibus utilissimus anno. Eenen nieuwen boeck van dobbel morisken seer oorbaerlyck voor goutsmeden borduerwerkers glaesmakers ende alderhande constenaren C hantwerpen balthasar sylvius ynventor et feecit.

Book of double moresques, never printed before now, most useful for all artists, as for goldsmiths, embroiderers, glassmakers, and this kind of artists. Year A new book of double moresques, very useful for goldsmiths, embroiderers, glassmakers, and all kinds of artists. C Antwerp. Invented and engraved by Balthasar van den Bos.
